name: TideChart

”Alexa, ask Tide Chart what time is high tide today in Palm Beach”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tide chart
Developer Terms of Use
des: This Tide Chart skill provides high and low tide times for over 3,000 cities in the United States, Caribbean and other locations for which data is available. You can ask by saying "Alexa, Ask Tide Chart for Myrtle Beach", "Alexa, Ask Tide Chart when is high tide today in Miami", "Alexa, Ask Tide Chart for Santa Monica tomorrow". You can also save your default location. If your location is not available, please email alexatidechart@gmail.com and we will try to get your location added.
priv:
